### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Create Category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Work",
  "description": "Work-related tasks",
  "color": "#FF5733"
}

### Get Category by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/{{category_id}}

### List Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories?page=1&page_size=10

### Update Category
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/{{category_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Personal",
  "description": "Personal tasks"
}

### Search Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/search?q=work&page=1&page_size=10

### Delete Category
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/{{category_id}}

### Create Todo
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive documentation for the API",
  "status": "pending",
  "priority": "high",
  "category_id": "{{category_id}}",
  "due_date": "2024-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

### Get Todo by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos/{{todo_id}}

### List Todos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos?page=1&page_size=10

### List Todos by Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos?status=pending&page=1&page_size=10

### List Todos by Category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos?category_id={{category_id}}&page=1&page_size=10

### Delete Todo
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos/{{todo_id}}

### Create Comment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "todo_id": "{{todo_id}}",
  "content": "This is a comment on the todo"
}

### Get Comment by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/comments/{{comment_id}}

### List Comments for Todo
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/todos/{{todo_id}}/comments?page=1&page_size=10

### Update Comment
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/comments/{{comment_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated comment content"
}

### Delete Comment
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/comments/{{comment_id}}
